The National Working Committee(NWC) of the ruling All Progressives Congress (APC) on Tuesday inaugurated the Screening Committee and the Appeal Committee for the party’s Edo State Governorship primary slated for June 22. The national chairman, Comrade Adams Oshiomole, inaugurated the committees at the party’s National Secretariat in Abuja. Chairman of the screening committee is Prof. Jonathan Ayuba while Dr. Rabe Nafiu will serve as secretary. The appeal committee has Prof. Abubakar Fari as its chairman and Dr. Daniel Wala as the secretary. Details shortly…